item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Sueña Conmigo 1 & 2 (Eiza Gonzalez/Nickelodeon) WAV/FLAC/M4A RIP
item.description:
Hi guys, hope you are doing amazing!
I am in search of these two Nickelodeon soundtracks in which Eiza Gonzalez plays the role of Roxy, a popstar, I am planning a masterpost of something cool that you'll see in some days, and i am mixing every Nickelodeon soundtrack (from America and Latin America) all in one folder/drive on the highest quality possible, from HIRES to some rare things in 128kbps mp3, i'll share soon when i finish it!

Sueña Conmigo: La canción de tu vida (2010)


Sueña Conmigo 2: Sigue Soñando (2011) (This album was released exclusively in Argentina, but later was put on streaming everywhere, please if you have an m4a copy from iTunes, or a WAV version, FLAC or even 320 mp3 share, thank you a lot, i just have 8 tracks i downloaded from Deezer in mp3, though i'm curious to hear this album in WAV or m4a )


https://www.discogs.com/es/release/14704974-Sueña-Conmigo-Sueña-Conmigo
https://www.discogs.com/es/release/12985104-Sueña-Conmigo-Sueña-Conmigo-2

Label of both albums: Nickelodeon / MTV Latin America (Paramount)
Published on CD by: EMI Music Latin (now Universal Music)
The 2nd album also had a bonus DVD edition which contained music videos for all the songs, like a visual album, but i just want the audios, no video needed, just in case, the videos are being uploaded on YouTube remastered in 4K and HD

thank you
